Package com.fasterxml.storemate.store

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StoreOperationCallback<IN,OUT>
    Interface that defines callback used for allowing atomic operations (usually of form "GET,modify,PUT") against store.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdminStorableStore
    Extension of the core StorableStore API, which adds methods useful for Admin tools, interfaces.
    Storable
    Class that represents an entry read from the backing BDB-JE store.
    StorableCreationMetadata
    Helper class for containing information needed for storing entries.
    StorableCreationResult
    Value class returned from "PUT" (insert, upsert) operations, to indicate actions taken.
    StorableDeletionResult  
    StorableStore
    Simple abstraction for storing "decorated BLOBs", with a single secondary index that can be used for traversing entries by "last modified" time.
    StoreConfig
    Simple configuration class for StorableStore
    StorePartitions
    Helper class for partitioning keyspace into single-access 'slices'
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    StoreException.InputProblem
    Enumeration of types of Input problems that are exposed to clients.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    StoreException
    General-purpose exception used instead of basic IOException, to allow catching of exceptions produced by store stuff, as opposed to underlying I/O system.
    StoreException.Input
    Specific StoreException subtype used when the problem is with input data passed to an operation.
    StoreException.Internal
    Specific StoreException subtype used for problems that are due to state of store itself, and not caused by caller's actions.
    StoreException.IO
    Specific StoreException subtype used for problems that are due I/O operations, but can not be exposed as IOExceptions for some reason.
